org.jboss.windup.reporting

Interface SourceTypeResolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaSourceTypeResolver, ModelSourceTypeResolver, XmlSourceTypeResolver

    public interface SourceTypeResolver
    Provides a way for addons to provide a source type for each FileModel type (eg, "java" for java types, "xml" for xml, properties for properties files, etc). The default implementation resolves some of these common types, and addons may provide additional resolvers.
